=== Setsusha ===
[[File:Onamochi-jinja, keidaisha.jpg|thumb|200px|right|{{center|Shinuchisha}}]]
There are the following four companies within the precincts <ref name="Explanation board"/>.
* Wakamiya Shrine - Enshrined deity: {{ill|lt=Kotoshirosu|Q8009611|WD=Q8009611|lt=Kotoshirosu no Kami|1=Kotoshironushi-no-Mikoto}}.
* Water Shrine - Enshrined Deity: {{ill|lt=Mizuhanome|Q8191796|WD=Q8191796|lt=Elephant Goddess|1=Mizuhanome}}.
* Konpira Shrine - Enshrined Deity: {{ill|lt=Kanayamahikojin|Q4387856|WD=Q4387856|1=Kanayama-hiko and Kanayama-hime}}.
* Inari Shrine - Enshrined deity: Inasoujin.

